      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i'm currently on a course of metronidazole for a nasty tooth infection... just wanted to check if its okay to have like 1 or 2 glasses of wine with dinner tonight or should i wait til i finish the meds?",
      "source": "evaluator"
